flowContents.comments: This NiFi flow ingests data from Salesforce, splits the incoming dataset into individual records, and enriches each record by adding or transforming necessary fields and attributes. After performing the required transformations and validations, the flow writes the processed and structured data into BigQuery,
flowContents.name: Salesforce_to_BigQuery

parameters.name: SalesforceQuery
parameters.value:
SELECT Id, Name, Phone, Website, Industry
FROM Account
WHERE Owner.Username = 'divija.garg613@agentforce.com'
  AND DAY_ONLY(CreatedDate) = 2025-10-01
